## Setup

### 1. Environment Variables

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in your values:

```powershell
cp .env.example .env
```

Required variables:
- `OLLAMA_BASE_URL` — Ollama server URL
- `OLLAMA_MODEL` — Default LLM model
{% if has_vector_store %}
- Vector store connection variables (see `.env.example`)
{% endif %}
{% if has_cache %}
